    <title>Switched On</title>
    <link>https://www.pbsfm.org.au/program/switched-on</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#222222; font-family:calibri,sans-serif; font-size:11.0pt"&gt;Join your host, Emma Peel, for two hours of dusty, obscure, kaleidoscopic gems from the vinyl vaults of time. Spanning the 1960s until now, and digging deep around the globe, Switched On dusts off forgotten records and weaves them together to create soundscapes that range from mellow and sublime to raucous and fever-pitched.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#222222; font-family:calibri,sans-serif; font-size:11.0pt"&gt;EMAIL: &lt;a href="mailto:thegirlbomb1@gmail.com" target="_blank"&gt;thegirlbomb1@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#222222; font-family:calibri,sans-serif; font-size:11.0pt"&gt;INSTAGRAM: @djemmapeel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
